# Layout Components

**Do not recreate components if they already exist in `src/LayoutComponents/`.**

Before building a new card, table, or layout element, check and reuse:

| Component | Use for |
|-----------|---------|
| `PageHeader` | Page title + avatar icon + optional description (use on all doc pages) |
| `DocTable` | Any structured table (props, tokens, keyboard, ARIA, etc.) |
| `WhiteBgCard` | Principle cards, callouts — white bg, light border |
| `GrayBgCard` | Principle cards, callouts — gray bg, dark border |
| `DocTabs` | Overview / Usage / API / Accessibility tabs (with slide animation) |
| `CodeBlock` | Code snippets with copy |
| `ExpandableDocImage` | Doc infographics / large figures — click opens full-size overlay (Escape, Close, backdrop) |
| `PageWithToc` | Pages with "On This Page" TOC |
| `OnThisPage` | Right-side section nav |
| `ColorSwatch` | Color preview tile |
| `ComponentOverviewCard` | Components catalog — fixed-height white + dot-grid illustration band, theme-aware footer, 2-line description + tooltip when truncated |
| `SectionOverviewPage` | Foundations / Patterns / Accessibility / Content overview grids (search, Ready status, shared cards) |

Import from `../LayoutComponents/ComponentName` (adjust path as needed).

**When adding new layout components:** Add them here and to README.md LayoutComponents list.
